4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students delve into Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, mastering skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat analysis. The program features three live online classes weekly, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The course is available in English and Spanish, and no prior experience is necessary. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop